		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>When in danger, the magic in your blood itself can strike at your foes.</em></p><p>You can only use this ability while @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{Raging}.</p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Creature (30 ft.) - 3/Long Rest - Magical</p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 3d6 necrotic]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>*This damage increases to [[/damage 6d6]] at level 14.</p>",
			"chat": "<p>You can use this ability when a creature hits you with a melee attack while you are @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{Raging}. You target the creature who damaged you.</p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - 1 Creature (15 ft.) - Magical</p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d6 acid]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>"
